{
  "stem": "22979.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was the [? sauna ?] where the people were undress who came to live, I mean, the working, slave laborer.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And 95% went straight to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you have to look on day and night, seeing the flames high in the skies, and-- and the smell, and the clouds settled, and the ashes-- black, greasy, [? fat ?] on our faces.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I-- we worked 12-hour shifts in the barrack, but my work was later outside.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was sorting with four girls, Lutka from [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Keltze, ?] Reshka from Czechoslovakia, and Adela, and me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], you know, the pots and pans what people brought out, we had to inspect and sort because there was lots of food.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Let's see.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, schmaltz, you know, grease from goose, in big pans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were hiding their valuables.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had to take out everything and, you know-- to search that, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we didn't have to-- we couldn't throw away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Many were glasses were broken.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The good stuff, salami, cheeses, you know, durable foods, packages with sweets and so, went on one side.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The broken things, which were glass and-- and-- mixed with glass went to the [? lagerkuche, ?] to the lager kitchen, because for us, you know, it's good there too.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they didn't throw it away, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You [? chew ?] glass even anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that was my work outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I saw the coming and going, everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's the reason I could recognize so many SS because I was working outside.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And since Kanada had so many goodies, the SS men came-- and you know, the kapos of overall-- they wanted furs.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They took jewelry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were stealing there.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
